import React, {Component} from 'react'
import {Layout, Row, Col } from 'antd';

import LeftNav from './components/leftNav/leftNav'
import FavouritesCard from './components/favCard/favCard'
import './favourites.less'
/*
头部组件
 */
const { Content } = Layout;


export default class Favourites extends Component{
    state = {
        theme:'light',
    }

    onFavTypeChange = (favType)=>this.setState({favType:favType})

    render(){
        return(
            <Layout className="favourites">
                <LeftNav onFavTypeChange={this.onFavTypeChange}/>
                <Layout>
                <Content className="favourites-content">
                    <Row gutter={[16, 24]}>
                        <Col>
                            <FavouritesCard address='https://www.bilibili.com/'
                            title='Card title1' description='This is the description'/>
                        </Col>
                        <Col>
                            <FavouritesCard address='https://www.bilibili.com/'
                            title='Card title2' description='This is the description'/>
                        </Col>
                        <Col>
                            <FavouritesCard address='https://www.baidu.com/'
                            title='Card title3' description='This is the description'/>
                        </Col>
                        <Col>
                            <FavouritesCard address='https://www.baidu.com/'
                            title='Card title4' description='This is the description'/>
                        </Col>
                    </Row>
                </Content>
                </Layout>
            </Layout>
        )
    }
}
